{"type":"question","id":98,"title":"如何看待北京大学数名校友失联一事？","uid":204,"topics":[195,196,402],"contents":"【简要】11月9日晚间10时许，在北大校内百周年纪念讲堂附近，2018届北大毕业生、寻月行动的发起人之一张圣业，被十几名不明身份的黑衣人士绑架带走。据当时在场的北大历史学系2015级本科生于天夫回忆讲述，这些黑衣人士穿着大体类似，帽衫紧扣，佩戴口罩，在把张圣业暴力拖拽上车后竟畅通无阻地驾车离开。包括于天夫在内的其他在场同学或遭到殴打、被按倒在地后暴力踢踹头部，或因围观拍照被强制要求删除相关图像材料。同日晚，另外两名北大毕业生孙敏、宗扬几乎同时失联！<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n【相关链接】<br>\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/xiaoyoushilian-11-11\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/xiaoyoushilian-11-11</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/China-Secrete-Police-Beat-Kidnap-Peking-University-Students-untrusted fake 2049bbs-Police-Beat-Kidnap-Peking-University-Students-20181112/4654701.html</a><br />\n&nbsp;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n</a><div class=\"clearfix aw-vote-ui aw-article-vote disabled\"><a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/China-Secrete-Police-Beat-Kidnap-Peking-University-Students-untrusted fake 2049bbs-Police-Beat-Kidnap-Peking-University-Students-20181112/4654701.html</a><br />\n&nbsp;\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n</a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree\"><i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">22</b></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"aw-small-text\">2018-11-15</span>\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-question__item_id-98\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"icon icon-users\"></i></a>\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"toggle_disscusion($(this));\" data-id=\"98\" data-type=\"question\" style=\"font-weight:bold; color=#333;\" class=\"aw-add-comment aw-small-text active\" data-comment-count=\"1\"><i class=\"icon icon-comment\"></i> 1 条讨论</a>\n<div class=\"pull-right more-operate\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"aw-small-text\" onclick=\"AWS.User.share_out();\"><i class=\"icon icon-share\"></i> 分享</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"aw-invite-box collapse\">\n<div clas